# Each workspace owns its own env file:
#
#   apps/backend/.env       — backend + Prisma vars (see apps/backend/.env.example)
#   apps/frontend/.env.local — frontend public vars (see apps/frontend/.env.local.example)
#
# This root file exists only as a pointer. Copy each workspace's `.env.example`
# into a real `.env` / `.env.local` to get started.
